# 🎓 Student ERP System

A modern Student Management System built using Flask, MySQL, Bootstrap, Chart.js, and Python. The application helps educational institutions manage student records, attendance, marks, academic analytics, and PDF report generation through a clean and responsive dashboard.

---

## 📌 Features

### 🔐 Authentication

* Secure login system
* Session-based authentication
* Protected routes
* Logout functionality

### 👨‍🎓 Student Management

* Add students
* Edit student information
* Delete students
* Search students
* Student profile page

### 📅 Attendance Management

* Record attendance
* Track Present/Absent status
* Attendance analytics
* Attendance percentage calculation
* Attendance reports

### 📝 Marks Management

* Add subject-wise marks
* Academic record tracking
* Recent marks display
* Marks analytics dashboard

### 📊 Analytics Dashboard

* Total Students
* Total Departments
* Final Year Students
* Average Attendance
* Average Marks
* Department Distribution Chart
* Top Student Performance Chart

### 🏆 Results Analytics

* Student leaderboard
* Top scorer identification
* Class average calculation
* Student performance ranking

### 👤 Student Profile

* Personal information
* Attendance statistics
* Subject-wise marks
* Academic performance charts
* Attendance charts

### 📄 PDF Report Generation

* Download student reports
* Subject-wise marks summary
* Student information export

### 🎨 Modern User Interface

* Dark theme design
* Responsive layout
* Sidebar navigation
* Interactive charts
* Professional dashboard cards

